P(X_1^n=x_{1}^{n} \mid \Theta= \theta) &= \sum_{j_1=1}^3 \sum_{j_2=1}^3 \cdots \sum_{j_n=1}^3 P(X_1^n=x_{1}^{n}, Y_1=c_{j_1}, \ldots, Y_n=c_{j_n} \mid \Theta= \theta) \label{eq:marginal} \\
